{"tid":2065350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《經濟學人》：數據證實，民主國家比極權國家能夠更有效抗擊傳染病。民主可以救命！","createTime":"2020-06-15T13:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T01:10:34.000Z","uid":48040,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f590cc35bad65b5fbb0080ee0da34a76cf296f97","tid":2065350,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"中國一直吹噓自己係抗疫的世界典範，因為專制體制可以更好監控人民及控制疫情。<br />\n<br />\n但事實係點？<br />\n<br />\n《經濟學人》研究發現，根據過去60年的數據顯示，民主制國家相比極權國家能夠更加有效抗擊瘟疫。下圖顯示民主及非民主國家在過去60年中瘟疫死亡率。淺藍色線是非民主國家，深藍色是民主國家。<ins>係同等的經濟發展程度下</ins>，非民主國家的死亡率高於民主國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPQQStb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPQQStb.jpg&h=f0b11f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2020/06/06/democracies-contain-epidemics-most-effectively\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fgraphic-detail%2F2020%2F06%2F06%2Fdemocracies-contain-epidemics-most-effectively&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=dc05efb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.economist.com/graphic-detail/2020/06/06/democracies-contain-epidemics-most-effectively</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">藍絲：我寧願得傳染病而死，都唔想要民主！</span><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlXPiafyjLc&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7lznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=121aa58d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc</a>"},{"pid":"cf52d8eded114332605012f87f48e8fdbbaa8e73","tid":2065350,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets